BirthData.DetailedNotes: Football player. Paraplegic from motorbike accident, in wheelchair, has not surrendered. Most accessible player for various functions. Has paid dues to the community, wants to adjust to new way of life. Laugh filled the locker room, daredevil, not looking for sympathy. Not really famous but nearly $200,000 raised for his medical expenses and . create a trust fund for him. NYT 12/73. .
